arStrings.szText:
Moving with a {c_important}Mobility{/c} Skill or {c_important}Evade{/c} spawns {c_important}{u}Storm Feathers{/u}{/c} along behind you.

{c_important}{u}Storm Feathers{/u}{/c} now drop from the sky as they are spawned, each dealing {c_random}[(Owner.Weapon_Damage_Min_Total + Owner.Weapon_Damage_Delta_Total) * Affix_Value_1 * (1+Owner.Bonus_Percent_Per_Power#Spiritborn_Feather_Spawn)]{/c} Lightning damage on impact.

Moving with a {c_important}Mobility{/c} Skill or {c_important}Evade{/c} spawns {c_important}{u}Storm Feathers{/u}{/c} along behind you.
